snippet.title: Sweet Elite - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Sweet Elite is a dating sim inspired by the popular Japanese Otome genre. Flirt with students and uncover Arlington Academy's deepest, darkest secrets. Will you be able to find out about the truth? Or will the pressure be too much for you to handle? It’s up to you!

NOTE: This is a re-upload where we fixed Ellie's name. Thank you to everyone who pointed it out to us!

PLAY THE GAME: www.sweetelitegame.com
Official Fan Discord Community: https://discord.gg/wsyRnKa
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/sweeteliteof...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SweetEliteGame
Tumblr: http://sweetelitegame.tumblr.com/
